!! Refactor wikitext chat

Chat mode with `output-mode: markup` — the LLM receives raw wikitext source via the `raw-wikitext` context template. Interactive session for refactoring wiki templates.

''Settings covered:'' chat mode, `output-mode: markup`, `output-target: display`, `inject-as: user-message`, tools enabled

```
<$llm-chat
  chatTiddler="$:/temp/rimir/llm-connect/examples/refactor-chat"
  tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
  systemPrompt="You are a TiddlyWiki expert. Help refactor and improve wikitext."
  tools="[tag[$:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/tool]]"
  contextTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/context-templates/raw-wikitext"
/>
```

!!! Live demo

